string-array.name: rat_en
string-array.item: You live in abundance. Do not begreedy otherwise you can become muddle.Beself reliant and conceited.
You are coward, lovable,gentle,abundant support from key people,generous and intelligent.
Be calm when come to catastrophe.Content is happiness. Be successfulin later year.
You have a poor and busy life. Be dependent on yourself. Be careful ofvilains. Canbe helpedby understandinghusband or loving wife and be successful in the middle aged year.

string-array.name: rat_zh
string-array.item: 当食之间，丰衣足食，如食量大，往往心生糊涂。自强心高,依命为正。
当胆大怕惊，终是小胆略,一生令人可爱，文雅温和，可得贵人多助，处世大方，脑海聪敏。
大则不平之事，能致死于非命，小则不平之事，可能出家，次之必成庸人。只是平心静气，知足常乐，晚年兴旺。
一生衣禄轻淡，劳碌奔波，不得贵人，处处遇难，不时小人捣乱，惊险重重得良夫贤妻扶助，中年出头。

string-array.name: cattle_zh
string-array.item: 待时出力，虽目前运滞，后日当有福，自有大用。
此人闻惊迫急，心猿意马，时欲出头肯干，不得其权，自我心强，一生胆大，无人能阻。
自由自在，到处可居无难，虽有些险岩风波，得能彼岸，他日自有盈余，独立心强。
忙忙碌碌，东走西奔，劳苦无休息，名不得时。

string-array.name: cattle_en
string-array.item: Although have the bad fortune, you will certainly be lucky and be successful in the future.
You are fiery, willing to work hard, but not good brains.You are pride and great courage, not afraid of anyone.
You live comfortable, able to adapt to the environment. Despite the some small difficulties encountered, but can be overcome. Very independent, and doubtless will be successful.
You are always very busy and work hard, but have no time to rest.

string-array.name: tiger_zh
string-array.item: 万象更新，虎跃虎威，名扬四海，家运隆昌，富贵吉祥，子孝孙贤。
自成权威，受人敬仰,冲天之势 立大功劳 青云有路 当际风云之会，必承雨露之恩，门庭新气象，堂宇换规模。
自食其力，有尊严风度 进退能自由，文武兼能，胆略过人，建立基业 性格刚强，白手成家 富贵成功。
脾气刚强 意志坚强，跋山涉水之苦 如折枝之易，赴汤蹈火之难，在所有辞，能克服万难，凡事可成矣。

string-array.name: tiger_en
string-array.item: You are very famous person, be born with a silver spoon in one's mouth. Grandchildren are fealty.
Be Successful in your life. Be highly esteemed. Have meris and achievements.
You are independent, have royal bearing, as a man one should afford to take up things and let them go easily. Be versed in both civil and military affairs. Excel in courage. Be ; successful.
You are a man of castiron will, be firm of purpose, can endure hardships .Having overcome countless hardships.Succeed in everything.

string-array.name: rabbit_zh
string-array.item: 奔波用功 忙忙碌碌，终日若得，尚称命运高
聪敏活泼，有冲天之势，如月之恒，如日之升，智略权谋，势如破竹，凡谋必遂，能成大业，一生幸福长发其祥
事业顺利发达，经营风顺，受人重视，有宇宙之大精神 互助合作，处世有情，待人接物，恭恭有礼 大吉大利
男女聪敏显耀，逍遥自在，清高显耀，青云之志，白屋之人，不难求望，诸凡遂心。

string-array.name: rabbit_en
string-array.item: You live a busy life，be studious,lacking good fortune.
You are intelligent, lively, be a born leader. Have menits and achievements.Full of resource and astuteness,succeed in everything. You will be happy in your life, longevity.
Succeed in you business. You are admired greatly by others.Be tolerant. Dedicated,reliable and team player leader. The way you get along with people is courteous.
You are inteligent, free and unrestrained.Profess to be aloof from politics and material pursuit. Although leading a virtuous life, you have great ambition.

string-array.name: dragon_zh
string-array.item: 志向远大，努力即能成功,经常救助他人，遇事易有波折。
谋事难，病弱身;进退维谷,有破几之苦
事事成就，福禄悠久。胆量才谋过人，健康，有德望，功利荣达
英杰才人，云游四海，乐于交友;连科及第一举成名，享自然之幸福。

string-array.name: dragon_en
string-array.item: You are ambitions,make efforts that can be successful, often help others, and do things not smoothly.
You do things difficulty, have an ilness body.
Do things suocessful, have a happy life.You are resourcefulness, health,will succeed in business.
You are talent,like to travel and making friend. You are good at study, and can be famous.

string-array.name: snake_zh
string-array.item: 四出有路，但经风霜之苦难免事事如麻，每每欲一-步登天，时机未到。
性情不高 志气萎顿， 作事懒成，独立难持， 总请高，亦是寒懦，禄薄福轻，烦事缠绵。
聪敏巧能，一举成名，为国之贤，功在四方，利达三江，能成大事大业，多劳多功，精神爽快，谋事诸遂。
精气浩大，威震四方，雅量敦厚,秉性聪明，地位权贵至高，有大志大能，侠义心肠，众人敬仰，受天之福。

string-array.name: snake_en
string-array.item: You have many things to do in your life. You need to wait for your time to come.
You are lazy to work,like to do things by yourself. You do not have much money, and have to face many troubles.
You are smart, famous, succeed in business,happy spirit, do things smoothly.
You are smart,at high authority position. You are ambitions, admired by others, lucky by nature.

string-array.name: hourse_zh
string-array.item: 活龙活虎,欣欣向荣，一生少得尝 新之机。为人表里如一，品德性正，缄默寡言，喜欢交友，欢乐人生。
创基立业，千辛万苦，家道兴隆 福禄得长生。
灵感过人，聪敏至极，技巧艺术超人，有日必得贵人助，诱人之力特强,一生无大灾害。清平闲静，安乐少愁。
技艺智谋过人，文武兼全,胆大心虚，德高义衙，感情和合，有志气，凡事逐渐成功，俊气才能，英杰才人。

string-array.name: hourse_en
string-array.item: You have active force.You are silence, good person, like making friends, have a happy life.
You work very hard to have a successful carrier. You will have a long life.
You are smart, siled, others will help you in your life.You are at bractive, have no disasters in your life.
You are smart, intelligence, ambitious,do things successful.

string-array.name: sheep_zh
string-array.item: 能免于是非纷争，但天灾地变常遇, 晦气多多。
聪敏出众，财源利达，万事吉祥，衣食必侠，富贵健康，享自然之幸,名利双全，能成大事业。
财丰利足，权势必高，所谋如意,出言有音，意志坚定，脚踏实地 能统率众人，受人之难，亦受敬仰。
受天之福 名种荣达，进退无难，处世和平，合谋志同道合，言而有信; 家运隆昌，荣华一世 晚享子福。

string-array.name: sheep_en
string-array.item: Avoid conflict, but you face many disasters in your life.
You are smart, wealth had health,succeed in business, and gain both fame and wealth， notworried in your whole life.
You are rich and have power, can be a good leader and admired by others.
You are lucky by nature, have a peace life, rich and have a happy family.

string-array.name: monkey_zh
string-array.item: 活跃力甚佳，精神爽快，事业出外，浮沉小病难免。
多忧惊怪，难化愚顽，虽有雨露之因 官居不久，而事宜囊箧空虚。
才能智技过人，江湖有伴，乡邻有田，婚姻美满，终身是幸，稼穑难成经营可企，凡事顺来逆去，改祸呈祥，前途光明。
东奔西跑，赴汤蹈火，奋斗有企，衣禄轻淡,待人接物 恭敬有礼，进退自如 诸谋可成，是非口舌小有，一生承享自力自食，自求自谋也。

string-array.name: monkey_en
string-array.item: You have active force,generous spirit, good career, unavoidable ailment.
You are Easy to worry and be trouble,very stubborn. Although someone may help you in business, you need to proceed with caution.
You are smart, have many friends,rich, and have a happy marriage, a bright future.
You are a busy man, polite, succeed in your business, often have conflict with others, do your business by own.

string-array.name: chicken_zh
string-array.item: 具有敏锐的直觉，才智也不错，且精于打算，甚为健谈，因此颇受人欢迎。
是个爱好自由，十分厌恶束缚的人，凡事不肯让步，喜欢力争到底。出入自由,精神愉快，气满腔足，终身作事有成，心平义仁，到老求谋顺利，清高寒儒
是个勤勉而温和的人，但是凡事过于小心，做事缺乏魄力。朋友较少，生活的圈子也较窄，为人诚实,是最佳的总务人选
感情十分丰富又敏感,对于细小的事也会哭泣或发怒，也是一个喜欢计划的人，但美中不足的是缺乏耐心，常常前功尽弃。足衣足食，四处皆粮，不力可餐，秋光照景,优秀聪敏，元志操坚固勤勉自立，能有盈余，五谷满仓，大旺全收，一生衣食可卜。

string-array.name: chicken_en
string-array.item: You have keen intuition.Your wisdom is also good, very talkative,and therefore quite popular.
You love freedom, loathe bondage,all things not willing to concede, like strive to exactly.Succeed in business.
You are a diigent and mild person,but do things too careful. Less Friends,honest, you are the best candidate for general affairs.
Your affection is very rich and sensitive,a small matter may cause cry or angry. You like to plan things, but are lack of patience, often have been wasted.

string-array.name: dog_zh
string-array.item: 具有悠然的心性且重感情。需要默默努力，一步一步向前迈进，才能开创自己的锦绣前程。
一旦定下目标之后，却能接受而努力不懈，个性外向、乐观且开朗，人缘佳而受人爱戴。
精神旺盛，能将理想和现实划分清楚。在文化、艺术方面有特长，喜欢帮助朋友。
喜欢讲理论，好思索，时常以思想家自居，野心大，充满热情而又有积极的奋斗力。

string-array.name: dog_en
string-array.item: You have carefree mind and deep in emotive. Need labored, one step one step forward, to start your own bright future.
Once set a goal, you can accept and try hard. You are outgoing,optimistic and cheerful, popularity and beloved.
You have high spirit, can divide ideal and reality division clearly.You are good at culture and arts,likes to help friends.
You are like to talk theory, good thinking, often to pose thinkers,ambition, enthusiastic and positive struggling force.

string-array.name: pig_zh
string-array.item: 长生在望，聪敏至贤，威尊望重,利路亨通，有自然之幸福，名利双收，能成大事业。
能成大功，人杰地灵，再兴再望,家声克振，定家门第 秉性聪慧,有天赋之美德，精力充沛，吉庆终世也。
秉性聪敏，职位权贵高尚，虽出有章，但亦有此微困，立足实地，可成大志，无上吉祥。
衣食丰盈，一生不力自事，不迁就他之事，自专独裁，凡事一帆风顺，势力强大，吉祥通临，定然成功。

string-array.name: pig_en
string-array.item: You will have a long life, gain both fame and wealth， and to be a success man.
You are smart, will be a success man and revitalize your family.
You are smart and can be a powerful man.
You are a rich man. You can make decision by yourself. Everything in your life is going smoothly.
